<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM14">
<l>aṭittalatti ṉaṉṟarakka ṉainnāṉku tōḷu</l>
<l>muṭittalamu nīmuritta vāṟeṉ muṭittalatti</l>
<l>lāṟāṭi yāṟā vaṉalāṭi yavvaṉaliṉ</l>
<l>ṉīṟāṭi neyyāṭi nī</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That day at the site of [your] feet, why the way you broke off</l>
<l>the five [times] four arms of the Rakṣasa and the site of [his] head,</l>
<l>you peacefully bathing in a river on the site of [your] head, dancing with fire,</l>
<l>bathing in that fire’s ashes, bathing in ghee?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
